p>\n\n\n\n<p>Om du känner för det, kan du också skriva en grattishälsning i kommentarerna här, eller på <a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/marketing/2023/05/27/day-20-wp20-from-blogs-to-blocks/\">det internationella födelsedagsinlägget</a></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large has-custom-border\"><a href=\"https://sv.wordpress.org/files/2023/05/2023-05-27.png\"><img decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" width=\"1024\" height=\"602\" src=\"https://sv.wordpress.org/files/2023/05/2023-05-27-1024x602.png\" alt=\"Skärmdump från jubileumswebbplatsen wp20.wordpress.net\" class=\"wp-image-1527\" style=\"border-radius:10px;border-top-style:solid;border-top-width:1px;border-right-style:solid;border-right-width:1px;border-bottom-style:solid;border-bottom-width:1px;border-left-style:solid;border-left-width:1px\" srcset=\"https://sv.wordpress.org/files/2023/05/2023-05-27-1024x602.png 1024w, https://sv.wordpress.org/files/2023/05/2023-05-27-300x176.png 300w, https://sv.wordpress.org/files/2023/05/2023-05-27-768x451.png 768w, https://sv.wordpress.org/files/2023/05/2023-05-27.png 1176w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></a><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Skärmdump från jubileumswebbplatsen wp20.wordpress.net</figcaption></figure>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:69:\"https://sv.wordpress.org/2023/05/27/wordpress-fyller-20-ar-idag/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:73:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n